description:
Adventist health education is not only meant to equip medical professionals for the future. It is part of God’s plan to redeem and restore the world.

For this reason, Adventists in northern Nigeria gathered to pray for the new Jengre Adventist College of Nursing Sciences prior to its official opening. 

Learn more on ANN Weekly and find other Adventist news stories on our website, adventist.news.
fulltitle: Adventist Church Members in Nigeria Pray for the New Adventist College of Nursing Sciences Jengre
